      • removeShape

        boolean removeShape(S shape)
        Removes the specified shape from this sheet, if it is present (optional operation). If this sheet does not contain the element, it is unchanged.(从此工作表中删除指定的形状（如果存在）（可选操作）。如果此工作表不包含该元素，则不会更改。)
        Parameters:
        shape - the shape to be removed from this sheet, if present(形状-要从此板材上删除的形状（如果存在）)
        Returns:
        true if this sheet contained the specified element(如果此工作表包含指定元素，则为真)
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if the type of the specified shape is incompatible with this sheet (optional)(Java.lang. IllegalArgument例外-如果指定形状的类型与此工作表不兼容（可选）)
